data.description: Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this exquisite residence, masterfully built by Pulte Homes, is a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. As you approach, you're greeted by a stunning facade that hints at the luxury within. The rear of this magnificent home features a sprawling deck that stretches across the entire width, offering an idyllic outdoor oasis for relaxation and entertainment.  Step inside to discover a culinary dream in the kitchen, resplendent with a chic ceramic tile backsplash and harmonious floor tiles, set on the convenient second level. This space is not just a kitchen, but a hub of warmth and creativity, where every meal becomes a cherished memory.  Ascend to the third level, where the allure of the hardwood floors in the family room welcomes you. This space, bathed in natural light, is perfect for intimate family gatherings, complemented by the convenience of a stylish half bath.  The basement level unfolds as a haven of tranquility with plush Berber carpeting. It houses a spacious storage/utility room alongside an additional living area. This level also boasts a great area for potential office space, ideal for those who work from home, and provides a walk-out to the beautifully landscaped rear yard.  The garage is a masterpiece in itself, featuring drywalled, painted walls, and a specialized flooring solution that elevates it beyond mere functionality.  A significant upgrade to the home came in May/June 2023 with the installation of a new roof, complete with a lifetime transferable warranty, offering both style and security.  The private quarters on the upper fourth level are nothing short of a retreat. Here, three elegantly appointed bedrooms await, including the luxurious primary suite. Two full baths exude spa-like tranquility, ensuring a serene start and end to your day. The convenience of having laundry facilities on this level cannot be overstated, adding to the home's thoughtful design.  In every corner, this home whispers quality and sophistication, waiting to embrace its new owners with open arms and the promise of countless happy memories.
